I think this could be removed.

Also this close() will call scheduleCompletePendingTasks() which again try to acquire the semaphore.
scheduleCompletePendingTasks() ": This function calls
reactor.stop();
reactor.process();
shouldn't this be called in reverse order i.e.  call reactor.process() first. ?

